{"tid":2239504,"cid":22,"subCid":0,"title":"（求救）想買冷風機","createTime":"2020-10-12T03:44:29.000Z","updateTime":"2020-10-12T07:05:05.000Z","uid":8060,"like":0,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":6,"replies":[{"pid":"12f5887bcab1fc5f226eaf6840e06c40940ca113","tid":2239504,"uid":8060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T03:44:29.000Z","msg":"依家有個200尺的地方，但係只有一部半匹既分體式冷氣機<br />\n<br />\n如果要換一部兩匹既，人工貴之餘工序都好麻煩，因為條雪種喉走幾個單位<br />\n<br />\n有無人試過買冷風機？有涼快感比風扇涼已經接受，feel到凍就更加好，咩牌子或者model會推薦？或者有無比冷風機更好的選擇？<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n（我就黎熱死喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />）"},{"pid":"5090d12ca67fc20b159d73922b42520e60a9d83e","tid":2239504,"uid":22362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T04:01:12.000Z","msg":"我建議你咪搞<br />\n好易滋生細菌"},{"pid":"e78348acd37a08c9a1b03b947e3e0ed8c6e95e97","tid":2239504,"uid":13149,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T04:14:08.000Z","msg":"冇撚用"},{"pid":"fc5b3a53cb440efe6e1b54a4c502dc65a58994ad","tid":2239504,"uid":13149,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T04:15:02.000Z","msg":"買部坐地式冷氣機好過啦"},{"pid":"333280770a9caa8ba7bb327219684b08ef908fb2","tid":2239504,"uid":8060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"5090d12ca67fc20b159d73922b42520e60a9d83e","tid":2239504,"uid":22362,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T04:01:12.000Z","msg":"我建議你咪搞<br />\n好易滋生細菌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-10-12T04:20:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />但係我又想比風扇涼啲"},{"pid":"77e28e3d524bed740e09b4a201c36885d98b9216","tid":2239504,"uid":8060,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"